dct_description_sm: Outside cover of map for Gloucester County published by the county's board of Freeholders. This side features a Historical Sketch of Gloucester County and descriptions the county government, services, agriculture, roads, industry and schools. There is also a list of each freeholder and their town of residence. One drawing and six photographic illustrations.
dct_publisher_sm: Gloucester County Board of Chosen Freeholders
